snippet.textDisplay: When a true lover of God goes into a tavern, the tavern becomes his chamber of prayer, but when a wine bibber goes into the same chamber, it becomes his tavern. snippet.textDisplay: I lose myself completely to the tune, lyrics, sitar-bass-drum, the overall composition just takes my breath away every time. Every musician involved with this particular piece has created something which will remain long after they are all gone. What can i say that can even come close to describe what happens to one's soul when this music comes blasting out. It pours divine love into my soul. Abida Parveen my eternal respect and gratitude. Love from Bangladesh.
